data.description: This rambler is absolutely stunning! It's been so well taken care of and has all the fancy features you could want. The neighborhood is super safe and quiet, plus it's just a short walk to Lake Minnetonka. The 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms make it perfect for a family. The living room and open-concept kitchen are perfect for hosting get-togethers. The kitchen has a sleek design, lots of counter space, and stainless-steel appliances. Plus, there's plenty of storage and a big center island. And don't forget about all the recent upgrades that make it even better. It's also in a great location near lakes, parks, trails, and award-winning Westonka schools. It's a real gem!
